data.name: HowCanIAddNewMember
data.value: How can I add new member?

data.name: HowCanIAddNewMemberAnswer
data.value: 1. Enter the Chat page. 2. Click icon that located on top left corner of navigation bar 3. Select Add new contact button. 4. Scan the QRcode. 5. Click on Save button.

data.name: HowCanIChangeDurationOfMessage
data.value: How can I change duration of message?

data.name: HowCanIChangeDurationOfMessageAnswer
data.value: 1. Click on menu icon which is located on right corner of bottom navigation bar. 2. Enter Display page. 3. The user can change duration of message from display page.

data.name: HowCanICreateNewGroup
data.value: How can I create new group?

data.name: HowCanICreateNewGroupAnswer
data.value: 1. Enter the Chat page. 2. Click icon that located on top left corner of navigation bar. 3. Select Add new group button. 4. Select users for the new group. 5. Write name of group. 6. Click on Save button.

data.name: HowCanISetLimitVisibilityOfNumberOfMessage
data.value: How can I set limit visibility of number of message?

data.name: HowCanISetLimitVisibilityOfNumberOfMessageAnswer
data.value: 1. Click on menu icon which is located on right corner of bottom navigation bar. 2. Enter Display page. 3. The user can set a limit for number of visible message from display page.

data.name: HowDoUserCanEditNameOfAnotherUser

data.value: 1. Go to the chat page. 2. Click on the chat for 2 second which user wants to edit. 3. Click on edit button which appears on right corner of navigation bar.

data.name: HowDoUserCanEditProfile
data.value: How do user can edit his/her profile?

data.name: HowDoUserCanEditProfileAnswer
data.value: 1. Go to the chat page. 2. Click on profile icon which is located on middle of bottom bar. 3. User can edit his/her name and photo, share public key, export private key by using profile page.
